des:
HU1 Radio is your college radio station for broadcasting 24 hours a day from our broadcast suite broadcasting around Hull and Holderness and online at www.hu1radio.tk.

We've been on the air since October 2016 running test transmissions but officially launched on New Year's Eve 2019 and everyday we bring you a unique mix of great music from the 80s to now along with all the local news and information about what's going on in this part of the world.
